metadata.name: Nothingness has emerged from Something.
metadata.description:
Poem and Image created by AI.

Treatment 1/7

GENESIS. 

"Nothingness has emerged from Something.  
The only thing that unifies these two states are that Nothing and Something both annihilate.

Nothing is a 'thing', Something is not.

It is the absence of a thing that makes one a thing and the other an absence of a thing.

Therefore, the two can never become one.  
embraces uncertainty"

New series and collection by OG AI True Face.  
New special collection in eth.
